title: Buying T206 Different Backs: Tim Jordan, Dahlen (Brooklyn), Walsh, Wheat, +++
author: SethY

posts.post_title: Buying T206 Different Backs: Tim Jordan, Dahlen (Brooklyn), Walsh, Wheat, +++
posts.post_content:
I am looking to expand my collection of backs for my T206 sets. I will list what I am buying below.

Tim Jordan (portrait especially)- any high grades and rare backs at any grade
Ed Walsh- rare backs.
Bill Dahlen (Brooklyn only)- high grades and rare backs
Zack Wheat- low grade rare backs, high grade at a fair price is possible.
Nap Rucker- Portraits of high grade!


I am also looking to buy nice portraits of other Chicago and Brooklyn players, preferably what would be referred to as "blazers" and ones that present well. Looking for graded PSA 4 - PSA 6 or their equivalent.

Seth
